race.description: Picklebet's Get Your Pickle On Handicap (Bm52)
race.comment: ROSIE'S PROPHECY (12) doesn't win out of turn but has placed in half her starts. This is a suitable assignment and can get the job done. O'REG (3) progressed nicely last time out to finish just 1.5 lengths from the winner in second over at Wagga Riverside. Not much tougher this time and on his best form he is capable of a big performance. ELLMAKNIFICO (1) will be doing his best work late. Was always going to be beaten for speed last start at Tatura over 1000m. Six furlongs much more to his liking. MAGNEA (5) has less convictions than most in this field. Keep safe third up. CHAIRMAN'S CHOICE (4) boasts a solid record over this journey and draws well. Keeping safe.
